## 3. What the Local Codebase Implies

### 3.1 Current Architecture

```
SoulSpecLoader (Effect.Service)
├── Internal (error-throwing, caught by public wrappers):
│   ├── getSoulOffers(soulName)              — partial match + full list for suggestions
│   ├── resolveSoulPath(soulName)            — direct path → search paths → partial match
│   ├── getAllSoulsInternal()                — crawl SOUL_SEARCH_PATHS, find soul.jsons
│   ├── findMatchingSoulsInternal(pattern)   — regex filter on getAllSoulsInternal
│   └── loadInternal(soulPath, level)        — resolve → parse → progressive read → cache
│
├── Public (error-remapping wrappers):
│   ├── load(soulPath, level=2)              — loadInternal + catchTags + catchAllCause
│   ├── getAllSouls()                        — getAllSoulsInternal + catchTags + catchAllCause
│   ├── enumerateSouls()                     — getAllSouls + per-soul load(1) with best-effort
│   └── findMatchingSouls(pattern)           — findMatchingSoulsInternal + catchAllCause
│
└── State: Ref<Map<string, SoulManifest>>   — key = "${path}:${level}"
