| Cache key = `"${userInput}:${level}"` — same soul via "dev" vs "developer" = 2 entries, `souls × levels` blowup | Cache key = `path.basename(resolvedDir)` — all inputs for same soul map to one entry |
| `load()` does everything (I/O + parse + cache + filter). Repeat calls at different levels re-read from disk     | Split: `loadSoul` (I/O + cache write), `getSoul` (cache read + filter + auto-load)   |
