## 1. What the Change Should Do

**Goal:** Replace the existing 4-method public API (`load`, `getAllSouls`, `enumerateSouls`, `findMatchingSouls`) on `SoulSpecLoader` with a clean 4-method API (`getSoul`, `loadAllSouls`, `listSouls`, `loadSoul`) that separates loading from reading, normalizes cache keys, uses `Effect.log*` everywhere, and never silently swallows errors.

| Design problem in v0                                                                                            | v4 fix                                                                               |
