| `load()` does everything (I/O + parse + cache + filter). Repeat calls at different levels re-read from disk     | Split: `loadSoul` (I/O + cache write), `getSoul` (cache read + filter + auto-load)   |
| 7 `console.debug`/`console.error` calls inside Effect pipelines (untyped side effects)                          | All `Effect.log*` — typed, composable, respects logging config                       |

### New Public API (exactly 4 methods)

| Method                        | Signature                                                   | What it does                                    |
| ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| `loadSoul(soulName, level=3)` | `Effect<SoulManifest, SoulLoadError, FileSystem \| Path>`   | Always from disk, upgrade-only cache            |
