| --------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| `Effect.flip`                     | Simple error-path assertions — swap error/success channels | Test 7 (existing)                                      |
| `Effect.either` + `assertLeft`    | Dual-path tests — handle both success and failure          | `~/.effect/test/Effect/error-handling.test.ts:52-57`   |
| `Effect.exit` + `deepStrictEqual` | Full Cause introspection (defects, interruptions)          | `~/.effect/test/Effect/error-handling.test.ts:103-113` |
| `Effect.option`                   | When null-on-error is genuinely needed (production code)   | Effect docs — preserves defect propagation             |
| `Effect.ignore`                   | Non-critical cleanup — suppress all including defects      | Prefer over `catchAll(() => Effect.void)` for cleanup  |

