## Gaps

1. **Effect v4 naming**: The v4 renaming (`catchAll` → `catch`, `catchAllDefect` → `catchDefect`, `catchAllCause` → `catchCause`) is documented but the pi-soul-agent codebase appears to be on Effect v3 (uses v3 names). The patterns are the same; only names change.

