# Synthesis: Phase 1 Findings for DRY/Optimization of `src/loader.ts`

Date: 2026-05-16
Context: TP-010 commit de209a3f
Sources: 01-researcher-external.md, 02-scout-local.md, 03-researcher-tradeoffs.md
