5. `BadArgument` handler (loadSoul)
6. `SystemError` handler (loadAllSouls)
7. `BadArgument` handler (loadAllSouls)
8. `loadAllSouls` zero-results fallback (in flatMap)

**Preserved inline:** `SoulNotFoundError` handler — only site using the `soulName` field.

**Why this form:** `Data.TaggedError.fromCause()` is NOT available in Effect v3.21.2. A custom helper is the recommended approach per the tradeoff analysis.

