  return yield * Effect.fail(new SoulLoadError({ message: "No souls found in any search path." }));
}
```

**After:** as a pipeline step at `loader.ts:336–340`:

```typescript
Effect.flatMap((results: SoulManifest[]) =>
  results.length > 0
    ? Effect.succeed(results)
    : Effect.fail(soulLoadError("No souls found in any search path.")),
),
```

The `flatMap` only runs on the success channel, and it produces `SoulLoadError` on empty results. **Behavior preserved.** ✅

