5. **DRY pattern**: `Data.TaggedError.fromCause()` (PR #3935, merged) directly eliminates the `new SoulLoadError({message:..., cause:...})` repetition. `SoulLoadError.fromCause({ message: "..." })` returns a `(cause: unknown) => SoulLoadError` function usable with `Effect.mapError`.

